{"word":"G4796 - συγχαίρω - synchaírō - soong-khah'-ee-ro - Rejoice in","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συγχαίρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>synchaírō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>soong-khah'-ee-ro"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Rejoice in"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூடச் சந்தோஷப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to rejoice with, take part in another's joy"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G5463 - χαίρω - chaírō - khah'-ee-ro/5463\">G5463</a>; to <i>sympathize in gladness</i>, <i>congratulate:</i> - rejoice in (with)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2168 - εὐχαριστέω - eucharistéō - yoo-khar-is-teh'-o/2168\">G2168</a>, <a href=\"#/G2169 - εὐχαριστία - eucharistía - yoo-khar-is-tee'-ah/2169\">G2169</a>, <a href=\"#/G2170 - εὐχάριστος - eucháristos - yoo-khar'-is-tos/2170\">G2170</a>, <a href=\"#/G4796 - συγχαίρω - synchaírō - soong-khah'-ee-ro/4796\">G4796</a>, <a href=\"#/G5463 - χαίρω - chaírō - khah'-ee-ro/5463\">G5463</a>, <a href=\"#/G5479 - χαρά - chará - khar-ah'/5479\">G5479</a>, <a href=\"#/G5483 - χαρίζομαι - charízomai - khar-id'-zom-ahee/5483\">G5483</a>, <a href=\"#/G5484 - χάριν - chárin - khar'-in/5484\">G5484</a>, <a href=\"#/G5485 - χάρις - cháris - khar'-ece/5485\">G5485</a>, <a href=\"#/G5486 - χάρισμα - chárisma - khar'-is-mah/5486\">G5486</a>, <a href=\"#/G5487 - χαριτόω - charitóō - khar-ee-to'-o/5487\"